---
title: (Vegetarian) Crispy Mexican Cauliflower & Chickpea Tacos with Lemon-Chipotle Aioli
description: Cauliflower and chickpeas provide a super satisfying filling for these tacos that are as tasty as they are colourful. We’ve given them a super crispy, crunchy exterior that you’re going to love. Simply dollop with lemon chipotle aioli and get to munching. Arriba, arriba! Ándale!
